{"tid":2117000,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完足總盃四強既表現 今次冠軍係阿仙奴了","createTime":"2020-07-20T13:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T18:38:01.000Z","uid":84081,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"82e94968e1b9d192ebbb2117fbcf4528b0e1b528","tid":2117000,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"決賽係妓對車路士 <br />\n<br />\n首先阿仙奴係拎過最多足總盃冠軍既英超球會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次呢個決賽對碰山狗秒GOAL 藍絲 再入2-1 相信大家都唔陌生 <br />\n<br />\n其次就係四強表現<br />\n阿仙奴泊大巴打贏哥狗 雷斯狀態好 好多人話世一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林伯又係贏傳控 又係唔識教防守 = 有哥狗既缺點冇哥狗既優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果四強曼聯唔係拜利傷出 蘇查選擇換入馬思亞唔係麥湯 4231守唔到基奧特先有機會入波<br />\n所以林伯好大機會又係輸反擊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估計係SAKA助攻畀奧巴美羊入波"},{"pid":"7375ac2ed286f5896df3d7d88a64d1bf44ad6e60","tid":2117000,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:48:58.000Z","msg":"再講狀態 車要對利對狼隊仲要備戰R聯 依家奇兵嬌魔傷埋 中場中KANTE又傷<br />\n根本佐仔 高華錫 巴鳩利同MOUNT打到8月1號都好攰<br />\n阿仙奴唔駛考慮R聯 可以盡地一搏 加上冠軍有得踢歐霸又係一大鼓勵<br />\n<br />\n今次車路士仲要冇埋夏剎特 我諗阿仙奴贏2-0 合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72c7483f3bb74b5fb8d65b1c72efdd783eeda03","tid":2117000,"uid":21896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"上次fa cup final贏車仔 當時車仔正選後衛係雷斯"},{"pid":"ae03037f6043cb33307066ed2b776daaad6fc1f0","tid":2117000,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f72c7483f3bb74b5fb8d65b1c72efdd783eeda03","tid":2117000,"uid":21896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"上次fa cup final贏車仔 當時車仔正選後衛係雷斯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:56:30.000Z","msg